headline: Invenra Welcomes Dr. Alan J. Korman to Its Scientific Advisory Board
summary: MADISON, Wis., July 14, 2025--Invenra, a biotechnology company specializing in next-generation multispecific antibody discovery and development, is pleased to announce the appointment of Dr. Alan J. Korman, PhD, FAIO, to its Scientific Advisory Board (SAB). Dr. Korman brings a wealth of experience in immuno-oncology, having played a pivotal role in the development of groundbreaking cancer immunotherapies.
